ent%20he%20would%20use%20to%20craft%20a%20very%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-most-promising-jobs-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elucrative%20career%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20years%20later%20that%20I%20realized%20I%20might%20not%20need%20to%20be%20so%20involved%20in%20their%20messes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8c0693b-c085-446e-b582-afa18cfd95a4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20always%20messes%20to%20clean%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funplanned-pregnancy-age-42-while-marriage-crumbling-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emother%20of%20five%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20four%20boys%20and%20a%20girl.%20Given%20the%20size%20of%20my%20family%2C%20there%20have%20been%20plenty%20of%20messes%20to%20clean%20up.%20There%20was%20a%20fist%20fight%20on%20the%20walk%20home%20from%20school%20one%20afternoon.%20There%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20shoplifting%20episodes%2C%20such%20as%20when%20my%202-year-old%20son%2C%20who%20was%202%20years%20old%20and%20unbeknownst%20to%20me%2C%20grabbed%20some%20candy%20from%20a%20lower%20shelf%20in%20the%20grocery%20store.%20He%20didn't%20get%20caught%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20discover%20it%20until%20we%20got%20home.%20And%20then%20there%20was%20the%20day%20the%20police%20showed%20up%20at%20the%20door%20to%20inform%20me%20that%20my%20sons%20had%20shot%20a%20BB%20into%20a%20neighbor's%20screen%20door.%20My%20response%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20my%20children.%20They%20would%20never%20do%20such%20a%20thing!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20my%20children.%20Somehow%2C%20they'd%20procured%20a%20BB%20gun%20and%20hid%20it%20in%20the%20loft%20of%20our%20garage.%20As%20they%20huddled%20in%20the%20rafters%2C%20they%20goaded%20each%20other%20into%20taking%20a%20shot%2C%20which%20did%2C%20indeed%2C%20damage%20the%20screen%20door%20of%20the%20house%20behind%20ours.%20It%20took%20a%20while%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-childrens-lies-challenging-parenting-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20did%20sheepishly%20admit%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20their%20crime.%20It%20was%20a%20collective%20confession.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20which%20one%20took%20the%20actual%20shot.%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20they%20did%20not%20receive%20a%20harsher%20reprimand%20from%20the%20police%20officer%2C%20and%20I%20was%20too%20stunned%20to%20do%20anything%20more%20than%20take%20the%20gun%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229956d0e5-4956-4924-b49a-0ac561fea2ed%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheir%20messes%20don't%20reflect%20on%20my%20parenting%20skills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20parent%20wants%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20child's%20transgressions%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20minor.%20Each%20time%20mine%20got%20caught%2C%20it%20truly%20felt%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fas-a-single-mom-i-just-cant-do-it-all-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20reflection%20of%20my%20parenting%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20there%20comes%20a%20day%20when%20we%20are%20no%20longer%20responsible%20for%20the%20actions%20of%20our%20children.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20happened%20when%20they%20each%20left%20for%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20many%20parents%20continue%20to%20oversee%20their%20child's%20activities%20even%20after%20they've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudents-move-out-of-college-dorm-rooms-coronavirus-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20into%20a%20dorm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20chose%20not%20to.%20I%20was%20done%20with%20stressing%20over%20their%20exams%20and%20worrying%20about%20whether%20they%20were%20eating%20well%20and%20getting%20enough%20sleep.%20I%20never%20asked%20for%20access%20to%20their%20grades%2C%20something%20many%20parents%20who%20are%20paying%20tuition%20feel%20entitled%20to%20do.%20I%20certainly%20did%20not%20request%20that%20t