'%20bitter%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mom%20died%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20a%20group%20home%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20he%20could%20do%20better%20living%20with%20me.%20My%20family%20discussed%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20inviting%20him%20to%20move%20in%20with%20us%2C%20just%20as%20we%20would%20if%20one%20of%20my%20husband's%20siblings%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-heal-relationship-with-sibling-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebecome%20our%20housemate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20we%20welcomed%20him%20with%20delight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c7c6c22-ed73-4530-bddb-774327d22b65%5C%22%3EHe%20wants%20to%20work%20and%20feel%20useful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20former%20job%20coach%20for%20adults%20with%20intellectual%20and%20developmental%20disabilities.%20I%20know%20how%20few%20employers%20take%20a%20chance%20on%20hiring%20someone%20with%20a%20condition%20they%20don't%20understand.%20My%20brother%20wants%20to%20work%2C%20to%20feel%20of%20use%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20I'm%20eager%20to%20help%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-tough-for-every-generation-layoffs-great-flattening-careers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20job%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20some%20time.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20stay%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20I%20dropped%20my%20daughter%20off%20at%20her%20residence%20hall%20and%20turned%20Entertainment%20Director%20and%20chauffeur%20again.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20our%20local%20Parks%20and%20Rec%2C%20the%20YMCA%2C%20arts%20organizations%2C%20and%20a%20dance%20studio.%20I%20registered%20him%20for%20classes%20daily%20so%20that%20he%20could%20make%20friends%20and%20integrate%20into%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20community%20has%20responded%20in%20beautiful%20ways.%20Now%2C%20when%20Mark%20walks%20into%20the%20YMCA%2C%20trainers%20