m%20an%20American%20who's%20lived%20in%20Cardiff%20for%2020%20years.%20The%20wonderful%20city%20should%20be%20on%20more%20travelers'%20radars.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cardiff%20Castle%20sitting%20on%20grassy%20hill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904c48e599d46a4ccc138fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECardiff%20Castle%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Burns%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20an%20American%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-the-us-to-wales-fourteen-years-ago-2025-9%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Wales%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20made%20Cardiff%20my%20home%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20city%20center%2C%20you%20can%20explore%20a%20castle%2C%20watch%20a%20rugby%20game%2C%20or%20walk%20around%20a%20park.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECardiff%20is%20compact%2C%20easy%20to%20navigate%2C%20and%20full%20of%20friendly%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20never%20even%20really%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbucket-list-trip-london-tourist-activities-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisit%20the%20United%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Naturally%2C%20I've%20ended%20up%20living%20here%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20American%20who%20has%20made%20the%20capital%20of%20Wales%20my%20home%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20sorry%20I%20did.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECardiff%20is%20a%20vibrant%2C%20eclectic%2C%20and%20welcoming%20place.%20And%20it's%20relatively%20affordable%20compared%20to%20some%20other%20major%20cities%20in%20the%20UK.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20its%20charm%2C%20the%20city%20doesn't%20pretend%20to%20be%20something%20it's%20not.%20Cardiff%20lures%20you%20in%20with%20its%20cheery%2C%20unass